data.description: One block from school is where this 1 1/2 story home is located. Open kitchen/dining/living with a large screened in covered back porch to sit on and enjoy the fall evenings. Eat in bar in kitchen. Master bedroom and one bathroom downstairs with double sinks and large linen closet and two bedrooms with a Jack and Jill bathroom upstairs. Mature trees and storage building in backyard. Lots of storage in garage. Great neighborhood.
